title: 671: BITCOIN SKYROCKETING TO $5 MILLION PER BTC IS A REAL POSSIBILITY EXPLAINS S2F MODEL CREATOR!!!!!
description:
In a recent interview with Scott Melker (The Wolf Of All Streets), the Bitcoin S2F model creator PlanB, gave reasons why he believes BTC will trade as high as $5 million per coin in years to come.

And yes, the S2F models predict prices ranging from $1 million (for the normal stock flow model) to 5 million (for the stock flow x model),” PlanB explained.
